In &lt;outputDirectory&gt; you name a folder in target where will be dependencies. In &lt;manifest&gt; you should enter main class. In &lt;Class-Path&gt; you should enter the path in targer, notice that Maven will add version, in my case testlib.jar =&gt; testlib-1.jar

